summary: you know what I appreciate so very much? the way Taylor has so strongly advocated this era specifically for maybe the first time...
body: you know what I appreciate so very much? the way Taylor has so strongly advocated this era specifically for maybe the first time in her career that music/records should be made to be an event again… that it shouldn’t necessarily just be something that is released and never really spoken about… that instead the music should be celebrated..the releases should be eventful and memorable…. it’s just a wonderful concept and way to go about it all and I really just admire the way she thinks

summary: People are always wondering how I can listen to Taylor Swift all the damn time and never get bored. But they a have that...
body:
People are always wondering how I can listen to Taylor Swift all the damn time and never get bored. But they a have that SOMETHING which always touches my heart, make me feel extreme emotions and also Tay really got through all of these times and now she’s truly doing better than she ever was and that strengthens me, pushes me to never give up, just keep going, step by step. I could listen to a Taylor Swift song on repeat for a week.. I would still be obsessed with it. You know, there are a few songs I like for a week or two… And then I’m tired of listening to them cause they don’t have that SOMETHING. Like, every single Taylor Swift song literally screams I PROMISE THAT YOU’LL NEVER FIND ANOTHER LIKE ME!

@taylorswift @taylornation

Here’s a pic of me with the cutest and softest rabbit in the world named Snowball cause Tay has literally the softest heart in the world. There’s no chance she would ever let us down. Dude, I love you.
